# =======================
## Cloudflare Worker / Storage backend

# Which storage backend serves uploaded assets (chapter pages, patches, avatars).
#   disk | local      → backend's local disk (./uploads, ./img-cache)
#   r2   | cloudflare  → Cloudflare R2 via the Worker (needs WORKER_URL + WORKER_SECRET)
# Leave UNSET to auto-detect: R2 when both worker creds below are set, local disk otherwise.
# Set to "disk" in development to force local storage even if R2 creds are present.
STORAGE_DRIVER=disk

## Cloudflare Worker
WORKER_URL=your-worker-url
WORKER_SECRET=your-worker-secret
